Our Recycling Adventure
Our class is learning about recycling. Ms.
Rodriguez asked us to
re
use old paper for our art
projects. She would
re
mind us to
re
turn empty
bottles to the blue bin. Sometimes, we need to
re
write our stories using
re
cycled paper.
Last week, we took a eld trip to the
re
cycling
center. We learned how trash can be made into
new things! When we got back, we would
re
visit
our notes and
re
view what we learned.
Re
cycling
helps our planet stay clean and healthy!
